data.description: This raised ranch offers convenient single-level living, complete with a ramp leading to the front door. The primary bedroom includes an ensuite full bath and a spacious closet. The third bedroom is currently set up for use as a laundry room, but new owners have the option to relocate the laundry downstairs with some minor handiwork. Situated on a .45-acre lot, the property boasts a beautifully fenced front and back yard with mountain views from back deck. The basement level features a versatile fourth bedroom or den with a half bathroom, along with unfinished storage space, and a two-car garage. Additionally, the backyard includes a sizable (approximately) 25x17x12ft high carport, perfect for a boat or RV, and a large (approximately) 24x14 outbuilding that has power ran to it, could be used as a workshop. New metal roof in 2018. Buyers/Buyers Agent to confirm all information contained here-in.
